<D>__{go on.}
<C>__{judy}
<D>__{it was like someone had jumped into my head and watched what was being projected.}
<A>__{now judy completely has forgotten that the camera is there.}
<C>__{jimmy}
<D>__{and earlier, what you said about god.}
<A>__{jimmy zooms in the camera by remote. judy's distracted.}
<C>__{jimmy}
