<C>__{jimmy}
<D>__{because it's rare that i get to find someone that lets their emotions go. when a person is crying, i mean truly crying, or truly laughing or smiling or frowning or gasping. for a few seconds or minutes i get a chance to see that person's soul. and really, now that you've forced me to think about it. i think it's a very rare and beautiful thing to be afforded that opportunity.}
